Package org.quickserver.net.qsadmin

Contains all of the classes for creating QSAdminServer.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CommandPlugin This interface defines the methods that should be implemented by any class that wants to override default protocol of QsAdminServer or add new command specific to your application.
